## Automated vs. manual recap

**Agent-drafted (from stated inputs):** answer skeletons pre-filled from the
scope manifest, audit ledger, generated artifacts, and evidence directory —
each marked `agent-prefilled` with its source.

**Owner-run (required before submission):** confirming every answer
(`owner-confirmed` + date), all certification claims (§F — never pre-filled),
every N/A reason in §J, the live-wizard reconciliation in §K, and the
submission itself. This worksheet never submits anything.
